      "date": "2013-03-13 03:47:28.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/4cef148a-8b8d-11e2-aa18-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
